page.title: 13A DAY IN JENNY'S LIFE
page.content: I wake up at 7.00am and lie in bed for about 5 minutes.Then I get out of my bunk and dress I wash and then go into my brothers room to see the time,if it is past 7.30 I go down-stairs,if it is not past 7.30 I go back into my room for a while.I usually get down stairs at about 7.35. I put the kettle on,for I have to make tea for my mum and Dad.I have my breakfast and take the tea to my parents.I get ready for school and set of at 8.45.I catch the bus at 9.00 _,and I get to school in Ranskill at 9.20 and go straight into the hall for assembly.Assembly starts at 9.30 and fineshes at 9.55.We go into class and do some English.We go out for a play at 10.45.Afterwards we do maths.At 12.55 we have our dinner. After dinner we do a varity of things like art,science,ect.I go home 3.35, have tea and go to bed at 9.30pm.
